/* SDSLib 2.0 -- A C dynamic strings library
 *
 * Copyright (c) 2006-2015, Salvatore Sanfilippo <antirez at gmail dot com>
 * Copyright (c) 2015, Oran Agra
 * Copyright (c) 2015, Redis Labs, Inc
 * All rights reserved.
 *
